-- Shuttle Bus Fire in Eastern China Kills 24 People, Injures 19, Xinhua Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-07-04T23:52:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-04/shuttle-bus-fire-in-eastern-china-kills-24-people-injures-19-xinhua-says.html

          
          
             A fire on a steel company’s shuttle
bus in the eastern Chinese city of Wuxi killed 24 people and
injured 19 others last night, the official Xinhua News Agency
reported today, citing the local government. It didn’t identify
the steel company.  
          
          


  


        